SUMMARY:Thursday Morning Bible Study
DESCRIPTION:Join Us for Bible Study \nEveryone is welcome to be part of our weekly Bible study—a time to grow in faith\, ask questions\, and share in conversation. Whether you’re new to the Bible or have studied it for years\, you’ll find a friendly\, open space to explore God’s Word together. \nCome as you are\, bring your curiosity\, and connect with others on the journey of faith.
