SUMMARY:Adult Education: Creation Care History
DESCRIPTION:Join members of the Creation Care team\, including Ron Gunderson\, Jenny Hutton\, and Clare Nielsen\, to learn about the 10-year history of Creation Care at CPC\, see what has been accomplished with partners and volunteers (including restoration of an acre of land into the Woodland Sanctuary that serves both people and wildlife)\, and find out how you can get involved.
