SUMMARY:Children's/Youth Choir Rehearsal
DESCRIPTION:Calling All Young Singers\nDo you have children and/or youth who love to sing and would like to be part of Children’s or Youth Choir at CPC? New for this year–we are forming a Youth Choir for middle and high school students! \nElementary school students are welcome to sing in our Children’s Choir\, which will meet weekly\, directly after worship for 10-15 minutes. The Youth Choir will also rehearse weekly\, right after the Children’s Choir\, for 20-25 minutes. \nFor more information\, or if you are newly joining\, please contact Wendy Johnston at wjohnston@catonsvillepres.org.
URL:https://catonsvillepres.org/event/childrens-youth-choir-rehearsal/2026-04-26/
LOCATION:Catonsville Presbyterian Church
CATEGORIES:Children's Education and Programming
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://catonsvillepres.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_4857.jpg
END:VEVENT
