SUMMARY:Dismantling Racism Potluck & Presentation w/Rev. Ross-Allam
DESCRIPTION:Join the Dismantling Racism Committee for an evening of community\, conversation\, and learning on Saturday\, May 2\, at Catonsville Presbyterian Church\, 1400 Frederick Road\, Catonsville\, MD 21228. \nWe’ll begin with a potluck dinner at 5:30 p.m. in the Fellowship Hall (please sign up\, as space is limited to 100 attendees)\, followed by a presentation at 7:00 p.m. in the Sanctuary by Rev. Jermaine Ross-Allam. No registration is required to attend the presentation. \nRev. Ross-Allam serves as the inaugural Director of the Center for the Repair of Historical Harms for the Presbyterian Church (U.S.A.) and is a Ph.D. candidate in social ethics at Union Theological Seminary. His work explores the intersections of history\, justice\, and faith\, with a focus on addressing historical harms and advancing restorative practices. \nBring a dish to share (or just bring yourself)\, and come ready to engage in meaningful reflection and dialogue. All are welcome. \nREGISTER TO ATTEND THE POTLUCK HERE: Register to attend the potluck. \nSIGN UP TO BRING A DISH FOR THE POTLUCK HERE: DRC Potluck Dish Sign-up
URL:https://catonsvillepres.org/event/dismantling-racism-presentation-w-rev-ross-allam/
LOCATION:Fellowship Hall
CATEGORIES:Fellowship and Connection
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://catonsvillepres.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_3341.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260503T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260503T100000
DTSTAMP:20260420T215753
CREATED:20260420T181805Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260420T181805Z
UID:10008934-1777798800-1777802400@catonsvillepres.org
SUMMARY:Adult Education: The Weight of Glory
DESCRIPTION:C. S. Lewis (1899-1963) preached “The Weight of Glory” on June 8\, 1941\, during an Evensong service at the University Church of St. Mary the Virgin in Oxford. Delivered during World War II\, it is regarded as one of his most significant sermons\, focusing on Christian longing\, love\, and inherent human worth. Join us for a discussion of this rich and imaginative piece. The sermon text may be found here: https://www.doxaweb.com/assets/weight_of_glory.pdf.
URL:https://catonsvillepres.org/event/adult-education-the-weight-of-glory/
LOCATION:Library
CATEGORIES:Adult Education
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://catonsvillepres.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Bearwalk_CPC_10.18__253.jpg
END:VEVENT
